<div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-3">
<h3 class='text-dark justify-content-center'>Approximation of Numbers</h3>
</div>
<strong>Approximation</strong> is the system of using rounded numbers or figures to estimate 
the outcome of calculation. Number can be 
approximated to a certain significant figure or to the nearest whole number.
<br>
<strong>Example 1</strong>
<br>
<strong>Solution</strong>
<br>
