<br>
<strong>Solution</strong>
<br>
	(i) 24 + 18 = 42 ~ <strong>40</strong>
  <br>
	(ii) 82 – 43 = 39 ~ <strong>40</strong>
  <br>
	(iii) 6.2 + 3.7 = 9.9 ~ <strong>10</strong>
  <br>
	(iv) 8.5 x 4.6 = 39.1 ~ <strong>39</strong>
  <br>
	(v) 42 ÷ 3.6 = 11.66667 ~ <strong>12</strong>
<br>
<strong>Example 2</strong>
<br>
